            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Consider the availability of local spare parts and technical expertise to minimise future operational downtime."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "By prioritising technical specifications and regional suitability over the lowest initial price, you ensure a long-term asset that protects your bottom line. GenFix provides expert consultations to help match your specific load requirements with the most efficient hardware available today."
          }
        ]
