      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Whether you choose to buy or rent, ensuring you have a reliable power source is non-negotiable for modern business continuity. Our team can help model the costs for both scenarios to find the most practical path forward."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Essential Maintenance and Servicing Standards"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "A generator is only as reliable as its last service, making routine maintenance a non-negotiable part of equipment ownership. In the Brisbane climate, dust, heat, and moisture can accelerate the degradation of oils and filters, potentially leading to failure during a critical outage. Professional servicing ensures that all mechanical and electrical components operate within manufacturer tolerances to prevent unexpected breakdowns."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "ul",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Schedule load bank testing annually to prevent wet stacking and verify engine performance under full load conditions."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Inspect fuel systems for contamination or biological growth, which is particularly common in humid Queensland environments."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Maintain detailed service logs of all interventions as per "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "a",
                    "url": "https://www.cummins.com/parts-and-service",
                    "title": null,
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Cummins"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " or other major manufacturer maintenance guidelines."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Regularly check battery health and charging systems to ensure immediate starting capability when the grid fails."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Proactive care significantly extends the lifespan of your equipment and reduces the likelihood of expensive emergency repairs. GenFix offers structured maintenance programs tailored to the specific usage patterns and environmental challenges faced by South East Queensland businesses."
