        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Emergency Support and Power Continuity"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Brisbane is no stranger to volatile weather patterns that can disrupt the main electrical grid without any prior warning. Having a robust emergency power strategy involves more than just owning a generator; it requires a plan for rapid deployment and ongoing technical support. Reliable power continuity ensures that critical infrastructure, data centres, and cold storage facilities remain operational during the most severe summer storms."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "ul",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Develop a clear activation protocol for staff to follow during a power failure to ensure safety."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Ensure your site has a pre-installed manual or automatic transfer switch for seamless power transitions."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
